BACKGROUND.name = "Mechanicus Explorator"
BACKGROUND.description = "The vast endless stars have been your calling ever since your last databank wipe. The past you once had was long terminated for one can never feel home sick if they never truly knew where home was. You were an explorator upon one of the explorator fleets of the mechanicus. These fleets would traverse the massive galaxy in search for any knowledge that remained. Your past on these vessels have been your own personal secret for only when you wish to discuss your past yet how you ended up here with this group is an even larger mystery than your past. Few people can remember seeing the person ever board the vessel and even fewer know how he did so. The person has been here for far longer than anyone knows and his intentions are left only to himself. The only thing that can be certain is that the individual feels at home among the stars."
